\p
\v 1 “\w Nebuchadnezzar|strong="H5020"\w* \w the|strong="H5020"\w* king \w to|strong="H1934"\w* all peoples, nations, \w and|strong="H1005"\w* languages, who are dwelling \w in|strong="H5020"\w* all \w the|strong="H5020"\w* earth: \w Your|strong="H5020"\w* peace \w be|strong="H1934"\w* great!  
